{"lemma":"نَدُّ","slug":"نَدُّ","root":"ن.د.د","root_slug":"ن-د-د","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-د-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n39562","","n39566","n39567"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D8%AF%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"equivalent, peer, coequal, counterpart, rival"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/nidd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n39562","headword_ar":"نَدَّ","root":"nd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nad~N","text_ar":"نَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, &c.,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nidaAdN","text_ar":"نِدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuduwdN","text_ar":"نُدُودٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, L, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadiydN","text_ar":"نَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, L, Msb, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tnAd~","text_ar":"تنادّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took fright,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shied, and fled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ran away at random,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became refractory, and went away at random;"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2778},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ran away,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"broke loose, and went hither and thither by reason of his sprightliness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, L, Msb, K.) See also 6, below. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nad~a","text_ar":"نَدَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", contr.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a people)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assembled."},{"kind":"text","text":"('Ináyeh, MF.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nad~a","text_ar":"نَدَّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a word)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"deviated from the constant course of speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$a*~a","text_ar":"شَذَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as some say; as mentioned by El-Fárisee: but it is not of good authority, nor agreeable with the usage of Sb. (M, L.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","L","K"]},{"entry_id":"n39566","headword_ar":"نَدٌّ","root":"nd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nid~N","text_ar":"نِدٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", M, L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain kind of perfume,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, L, K,) well known, (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which one fumigates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, M, L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain wood with which one fumigates:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gaAliyapN","text_ar":"غَالِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as Z says, in the Rabeea el-Abrár,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a compound of aloes-wood aromatized with musk and ambergris and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nAn","text_ar":"نان"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) or (accord. to Aboo-'Amr Ibn-El-'Alà, T, L) ambergris,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EanobarN","text_ar":"عَنْبَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, L:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EabiyrN","text_ar":"عَبِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e., either"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saffron,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain mixture of perfumes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the copy of the T used by the author of the TT, if correctly transcribed by him:] it is not Arabic: (S:) or is thought by IDrd to be not genuine Arabic: (M, L,) many of the lexicologists, however, hold it to be genuine Arabic; and it occurs in verses of old poets; (MF;) but this does not prove that it is not an arabicized word. (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nad~N","text_ar":"نَدٌّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A high hill;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a hill rising high into the sky:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L:) of the dial. of El-Yemen: (L:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great hill"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akamap","text_ar":"اَكَمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"loam."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","L","K","Lth","Msb","TA","T"]},{"entry_id":"n39567","headword_ar":"نِدٌّ","root":"nd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadiydN","text_ar":"نَدِيدٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadiydapN","text_ar":"نَدِيدَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A like"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K) of a person or thing: (L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a like"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by participation of substance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"a more special term than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mivolN","text_ar":"مِثْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies “ a like by participation of anything: ” (the kádee Zekereeyà, MF:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing which does,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may, supply, the place"},{"kind":"text","text":"of another thing: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a like that is contrary,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"opposed, to another thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that opposes it"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yunaHAd~uhu","text_ar":"يُنَحادُّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yuxaAlifuhu","text_ar":"يُخَالِفُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in its circumstances;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Did~N","text_ar":"ضِدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ibohN","text_ar":"شِبْهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Akh:) and hence the first is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an idol; a thing taken as an object of worship instead of the true God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) pl. of the first,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anodaAdN","text_ar":"اَنْدَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, Msb, K;) and of the second,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nudadaA='u","text_ar":"نُدَدَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and of the third,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadaAy^idu","text_ar":"نَدَايِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa nid~u fulaAnK","text_ar":"هُوَ نِدُّ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadiyduhu","text_ar":"نَدِيدُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadyidatohu","text_ar":"نَديِدَتْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is the like of such a one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"hiYa nid~u fulaAnapa","text_ar":"هِىَ نِدُّ فُلَانَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISh, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She is the like of such a female;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISh, L;) but not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nid~u fulaAnK","text_ar":"نِدُّ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (ISh, L, K.) You also say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa nid~iY","text_ar":"هُوَ نِدِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadiydiY","text_ar":"نَدِيدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is my opponent with respect to the course that I would pursue, contending with me for a different course."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth, T, L.)       -A2-  See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nad~N","text_ar":"نَدٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","L","K","TA","Akh","ISh"]}]}}